    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>* Claire Ferguson was named operations director for a new British division of DVC Experiential Marketing, part of DVC Worldwide. Ms. Ferguson, who will be based in the new Berkshire, England, office, had been director for promotions at Launch Brand Marketing, Toronto.</p>
